INtroduction:

To make Restful API's:
1. Use Http request Verbs

Http request verbs: GET, POST, PUT, PATCH, DELETE

GET-->Read
POST-->Create
PUT, PATCH---> Update
    {
        PUT--Update datbase by sending entire new entry of databse
        PATCH--only sending piece of data that need to be update.
    }
DELETE--->Delets
    
2. Use specific Pattern of Routes/Endpoint URLs

Notes:

Client----API----Server
